Surprisingly Spacious Maisonette with Garden and Three Bedrooms in Amsterdam-Slotermeer. This surprisingly spacious and well-maintained maisonette of 68m² features a lovely, sunny southeast-facing garden and offers no less than three bedrooms. Located on a quiet street surrounded by greenery in the vibrant neighborhood of Amsterdam-Slotermeer, where city life meets the outdoors.

