At the front there is a spacious bedroom with enough space for a large built-in wardrobe.
The modern and fully tiled bathroom is located in the middle part and is equipped with a bath/shower combination, toilet and a sink. In the hall is also a spacious stair cupboard with storage space and a washing machine connection. The meter cupboard has also been installed here. 

